    public static class Types.TypeMapping<S>
extends Types.MapVisitor<S>
implements Function<Type,Type>
    An abstract class for mappings from types to types (see Type#map(TypeMapping). This class implements the functional interface Function, that allows it to be used fluently in stream-like processing.
